wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/Fitxes-ANG.pdf\">The Game of Knowing How to Look<\/a>&nbsp;from&nbsp;<a href=\"https:\/\/www.amazon.com\/gp\/product\/0253355036\/ref=as_li_qf_asin_il_tl?ie=UTF8&amp;tag=jamesclearema-20&amp;creative=9325&amp;linkCode=as2&amp;creativeASIN=0253355036&amp;linkId=fc3fdc7277311f90a8c09bf0b69b6eb6\">Complete Writings, Volume II: Collected Essays<\/a><\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"h-1-question-for-you\">1 QUESTION FOR YOU<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>If you met someone exactly like yourself &#8230;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>&#8211; same experience<br>&#8211; same resources<br>&#8211; same problems<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>&#8230; what advice would you give them?<\/p>\n\n\n\n\n\n<p>Until next week,<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>James Clear<br><em>Author of the million-copy bestseller,&nbsp;<a href=\"https:\/\/atomichabits.com\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Atomic Habits<\/a><br>Creator of the&nbsp;<a href=\"https:\/\/jamesclear.com\/habit-journal\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Habit Journal<\/a><\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>p.s.\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/jamesclear.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/10\/volcano.png\">I love your volcano<\/a>.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>3 IDEAS FROM ME I. &#8220;Maturity is learning how to start when you feel like procrastinating and learning how to listen when you feel like talking.&#8221; II. &#8220;Solve big problems early. Rebound after one missed workout, not a decade of inactivity. Repair a strained relationship the next day, not years later. Fix overspending before it [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"menu_order":0,"template":"","acf":[],"yoast_head":"<!-- This site is optimized with the Yoast SEO Premium plugin v20.5 (Yoast SEO v20.6) - https:\/\/yoast.com\/wordpress\/plugins\/seo\/ -->\n<title>3-2-1: On maturity, how to do exceptional work, and the connectedness of things - James Clear<\/title>\n<meta name=\"robots\" content=\"index, follow, max-snippet:-1, max-image-p